# Pitch / submission scratch (keep local, don't commit)
PITCH.md
SUBMISSION.md
docs/demo-script.md

# Tests (kept local, not committed — see chat history for rationale)
# Covers existing + any future Python test files / dirs at any depth.
# NOTE: Rust inline `#[cfg(test)]` blocks live inside source files
# (e.g. gateway/aegis-core/src/dedup.rs) and cannot be gitignored
# without editing source. Those few lines stay where they are.
tests/
**/tests/
**/test_*.py
**/*_test.py
**/conftest.py
.pytest_cache/
pytest.ini
pytest-*.xml
.coverage
htmlcov/
